data.description: Welcome home to 5760 Glen Oak Turn!! This four bedroom, two and half bath home, lays nestled in a cul-de-sac in the Woodspring at New Market, is ready for its new owner. Featuring an expansive open style floor plan once you enter the home. Natural light fills this home from the second floor with its two-story ceiling. The main level includes a first-floor owners suite with ensuite, along with an eat in kitchen and dining area. Upstairs features three spacious bedrooms, a massive loft space, and a full bathroom in the hallway. The unfinished basement is a blank canvas ready for this home’s new owner, which has a large laundry space with a washer and dryer included. Relax outdoors on a composite deck, with a fully fenced backyard with beautiful tall trees providing some good shade on those hot days. Large 2 car garage. Close distance to sporting fields, walking paths, tennis courts, three playgrounds and plenty of recreational space. Close to major commuter routes, shopping, dining, golf, downtown New Market, and only minutes to Frederick. Ready for immediate move in!!
